reviewText: Bought this video just because I have lowrider myself. Cool little video with a couple of sweet rides & pretty hilarious do to the people there. It looks like an ICP concert let out early. Also it's alittle older footage, appears to made in the late 90s early 2000s somewhere in Michigan.
A dvd throw back to the 90's.. Everything from Roadstars down to the Suzuki Samurai dancers.. CCE, Show and Go.. lots of good footage.
